<a href="/questions/283181-i-found-this-series-by-accident-and">I found this series by accident and immediately fell in love. Read them through on release and wanted to again, but due to my sight starting to fail I thought I&#39;d pick up the audiobook instead. Worst mistake I&#39;ve made in a while. Pete Bradbury&#39;s wet and nasally narration doesn&#39;t do this series justice,
