  <span id="freeText1300164338293911227" style="display:none">I read the early books with great pleasure they were an interesting take on fantasy but as the series progressed I found the rather pointed religious references started to spoil my enjoyment. I am not sure when I stopped but the volume was full of pointless violence against women with a lot of nauseating content which had little or nothing to do with the plot so stopped reading. Great shame as the main plot and characters were excellent and the books well written.</span>
