        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1200245881" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2536208397196692188"><b>Buddy read with my wonderful friend, Celise</b><br/><br/>I freaking loved this book!! Arlen, Leesha, Rojer, Bruna, Ragen, Cob, Leesha&apos;s father and Twilight Dancer were my favorite characters. <br/><br/>The book tells the story about 3 people, Arlen, Leesha, &amp; Rojer. It starts when they are younger until they are adults and how they find each other. <br/><br/>They live in a world where you have to be inside a Warded home or Warded circle etc, before night fall. This is when the demons rise and if you&apos;re not safe, you&apos;re pretty mu</span>
  <span id="freeText2536208397196692188" style="display:none"><b>Buddy read with my wonderful friend, Celise</b><br /><br />I freaking loved this book!! Arlen, Leesha, Rojer, Bruna, Ragen, Cob, Leesha's father and Twilight Dancer were my favorite characters. <br /><br />The book tells the story about 3 people, Arlen, Leesha, &amp; Rojer. It starts when they are younger until they are adults and how they find each other. <br /><br />They live in a world where you have to be inside a Warded home or Warded circle etc, before night fall. This is when the demons rise and if you're not safe, you're pretty much eaten!<br /><br />I can't describe how awesome this world is, besides the getting eaten part. I mean it's just like nothing I have read before! And yes, there are people I wanted to beat down, but that is all par for the course!! <br /><br />I really, really hope the next books are good because there are mixed reviews. I hate that because this is one of my new favorite books! <br /><br />Mel ❤️</span>
